I '''James Lee Burke''' (mibait Diciembre 5, 1936) metung yang [[Estados Unidos|Americanu]]ng talasulat da reng [[mystery fiction|misterio]], a pikabaluan dili king king kayang serieng [[Dave Robicheaux]]. Sinambut yang [[Edgar Award]] para king ''Black Cherry Blues'' ([[1990 in literature|1990]]) ampong ''Cimarron Rose'' ([[1998 in literature|1998]]). Mekatadua ne linto king cine ing tauan nang Robicheaux, a mumuna nang legen [[Alec Baldwin]] (''[[Heaven's Prisoners]]'') at kaibat i [[Tommy Lee Jones]] (''[[In the Electric Mist]]''). Sinulat ya muring pitung aliwang claseng novela ning crimen i Burke, aduang antolohia da reng makuyad a salita ampong apat a  libru nung nukarin ya tauan ing metung a bida, ing abugadung ibat [[Texas]], i Billy Bob Holland.

